~/Library/Android/sdk/platform-tools/adb logcat ActivityManager:I CurrencyCalculator:D *:S
adb devices
adb -s <device> shell
run-as xplr.in.currencycalculator

Build debug apk (signed and zipaligned)
./gradlew assembleDebug

Release
bin/release

Deploy apk
bin/install

Screenshotes
bin/adb shell /system/bin/screencap -p /sdcard/screenshot.png
bin/adb pull /sdcard/screenshot.png main-activity-screenshot.png

